    {
      "beat_id": "B01",
      "act": "HOOK",
      "narration_text": "Namaste. Liam, in for Bear. Angular-momentum algebra permits integers and half-integers. Orbital angular momentum uses only integers, while every electron carries spin one half. The difference is not the commutator algebra.",
