            "topic": "QUANTUM MECHANICS — ANGULAR MOMENTUM",
            "segment": "Why Spin-One-Half Exists",
            "greeting": "Namaste, Liam",
            "runningText": "separating algebra from representation and boundary conditions…",
            "output": [
              "The ladder algebra permits integer and half-integer j.",
              "Orbital boundary conditions select integer ell."
            ],
